Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.anagalacticruby.Product
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Item
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AudioPlayer, MoviePlayer, Widget

    public abstract class Product
extends java.lang.Object
implements Item
    This is the class that is the powerhouse of the program.

    A product's name, manufacturer and type are put into a constructor and then printed when the toString is called.
